Small game made with the Perlenspiel engine (http://perlenspiel.org).
It has been created for a private perlenspiel gamejam. The restriction was to use only 16x16 beads.
Check out the game: http://chrixko.github.com/Need-for-Beads

Controls: Arrow keys

The route is generated randomly. If you think its too boring try refreshing the page :D